Package org.apache.flex.compiler.fxg

This package and its subpackages contains classes and interfaces for compiling FXG.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFXGParser
    A IFXGParser parses an InputStream for an FXG document and builds a custom DOM.
    IFXGTranscoder
    Simple interface for a transcoder on an FXG DOM.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FXGConstants
    Constants for the FXG document format.
    FXGFileNode
    Temporary class to wrap a IFXGNode in an IASNode.
    FXGParserFactory
    A simple factory to create an instance of an IFXGParser implementation.
    FXGVersion
    FXGVersion is an enumeration of the different versions of FXG Specification.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description

Package org.apache.flex.compiler.fxg Description

This package and its subpackages contains classes and interfaces for compiling FXG.

This is mostly legacy code from the old mxmlc compiler.
